# About:
Al3x's Lanterns is a texture pack that completely revamps all kinds of lanterns and chains in minecraft. Perfect for enhancing all kinds of builds in your world.


![Lanterns](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/df78c36f45fdc5290c99d76366b5779a9ca0b3ca_0.webp)

# Features:
- New Lantern;
- New Soul Lantern;
- New Copper Lantern and variants;
- New iron and copper chains.
